@startuml network-scenario-2-vpn
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8

title **Scenario 2 — Home WLAN + Cisco AnyConnect VPN**

left to right direction

node "MacBook" as MB {
  [detect-network.sh] as DET
  [Proxydetox\n:3128] as PD
  [Claude CLI] as CLI
  [Cisco AnyConnect] as VPN
}

cloud "Home Router\n→ ISP" as HOME

rectangle "BMW Corporate Network\n(via VPN tunnel)" as CN {
  [PAC Server\nmuc.proxy-pac.\nbmwgroup.net] as PAC
  [Central Proxy\n(Squid/BlueCoat)] as CP
  [Firewall\n(URL category filter)] as FW #FFCDD2
}

cloud "Internet" as INET {
  [api.anthropic.com] as AN
  [api.github.com] as GH
}

' VPN tunnel
VPN -[#blue,bold]-> HOME : encrypted
HOME -[#blue,bold]-> CN : IPsec/DTLS tunnel

' Detection
DET -[#green]-> PAC : 1. DNS resolves ✓\n→ INSIDE_CN=true

' Traffic flow
CLI -[#green,bold]-> PD : 2. https_proxy=:3128
PD -[#green,bold]-> PAC : 3. fetch proxy.pac
PD -[#green,bold]-> CP : 4. CONNECT :443
CP -[#green,bold]-> FW : 5. URL check
FW -[#red,bold]-x AN : 6. **BLOCKED** ✗\n(AI/ML category)
FW -[#green,bold]-> GH : 6. **ALLOWED** ✓\n(Developer Tools category)

note bottom of MB
  **INSIDE_CN = true** (VPN provides corporate DNS)
  **Same firewall policy as onsite** — api.anthropic.com
  is blocked by URL category filter (AI/ML).
  api.github.com passes (Developer Tools).
  **Result: Claude Code ✗ | OpenCode (Copilot) ✓**
end note

@enduml
